captions.text: Homie, listen here I'm going to show you everything in Mexico!
Gonna show you the lizards, the palm trees, the mangos, all types of things!!
I also must say I won't be responsible for any items lost or damaged, you hear me?
So sir, if you ask me to take a picture of you...
And I take the picture and then don't know where your camera went...
YOU CAN'T BLAME ME!
I know what you're thinking. You can come from America and Canada and start racial profiling...NO.
Ready. Set. Go.
Start your day right. All types of fruit...
Pineapple. Watermelon. Whatever that bloodclat thign is. Cantaloupe. Melon.
And we wear white gloves to ensure there's no STDs on your fruit.
If you're a bloodclat alcoholic, no one is judging you here darling.
Have some Vodka for breakfast...
If you for some reason decide to bring a child on your vacation, firstly slap yourself...
Second, we have lots of food for them and we also have...
lots of banana dem.... mmmmm banana dem.
so many places to sit you see!
here.
You can sit in this chair right here.
here.
here.
So many activities for the youth...
but sometimes it gets a little intense.
why did you push me bro? You want to fight?!
You want to check mate?! No worries I'm going to bang your girl tonight...
So many games! Whatever this game is...
Table tennis and a sweater. I found a sweater!
$10 for the sweater. Cash only!
Maybe you have a girlfriend or boyfriend. Maybe you're mad at them? Or maybe you cheated on them...
Take them to this romantic dinner with a little bit of champagne!
No one says no to champagne!
What if you finish the champagne?? no worries. There's plenty more!
Swing on the hammock but don't forget all the alcohol from before...
cause you'll be drunk on the hammock like...
Trees! Trees! Trees...
OW MY FACE!
Don't injure your facial features my friend.
Want to stay fit? No problem! Water aerobics for you my dear!
Y..M..C..A
Maybe you think you're a mermaid and you want to swim in the sea? No problem...
It's plenty safe and someone is always on duty!
This tube.
Maybe you like this tree? so you want to sit right here...
Then this coconut is going to fall and intend your face so be careful.
The only place in the world where a man approaches you with a drink and says...
"Drink of the day for you honey"
And you better take that drink!...don't judge me.
We have plants, plants, plants, plants, plants and TREEEESSSS.
Look at this plant. It's so nice. A fuzzy peachy plant that's such a plant. Plants. YAY YAY!
If you don't want a lizard on your bum...
Don't come to Mexico.
If you're swimming and get thirsty, no problem! We have plenty swim-up bars...
but don't drink too much because your drunk self is going to jump in the pool and...
BLAAAA...your bum will drown.
You want to fight with water? Go jet skiing my dear friend.
You want to parasail?
You want to go snorkelling? NO PROBLEM!
Under the sea, with the fishies.
Okay! Hope you enjoyed the tour! Just a friendly reminder that tips are appreciated...
So leave me some money...
OH LOOK! This man gave me one dollar.
How much did your vacation cost? 10 000? You gave me one dollar?..no no that's fine...
It's all good...SHUT YOUR MOUTH.
I hope you enjoyed the tour. If you have any other kids that want to see the place, I'm here all week.
Hope you enjoyed Mexico. Don't forget Superwoman is back in Toronto and will makes videos every Monday and Thursday!
My dear angel, before you go...
Click thumbs up!
Comment below.
and please kindly click that beautiful subscribe button.
